DESCRIPTION:Join us on Wednesday\, June 3\, from 4-7 PM at Whispering Vine South Creek for a Ferrari-Carano whites tasting featuring four crisp\, textured and cellar-worthy bottles across Pinot Grigio\, Rosé and Chardonnay.\nTasting Fee: $25 per person (Buy a bottle from the tasting and your fee is refunded)\nFeatured Wines:\n- Ferrari-Carano Pinot Grigio 2024 (California) - $13.99 | Winery $35 - Lychee\, orange blossom\, peach and jasmine with mango\, orange zest\, melon and crisp acidity.\n- Ferrari-Carano Dry Sangiovese Rosé 2025 (Sonoma County) - $13.99 | Winery $17 - Strawberry cream\, watermelon\, raspberry and orange zest with cranberry\, white cherry and blood orange.\n- Ferrari-Carano Tre Terre Chardonnay 2023 (Russian River Valley) - $26.99 | Winery $35 - Apple\, pear\, lemon curd\, baking spice and vanilla-toned richness with a creamy\, balanced finish.\n- Ferrari-Carano Reserve Chardonnay 2022 (Carneros) - $29.99 | Winery $48 - Apple crisp\, caramel popcorn\, golden apple\, pear\, peach cobbler and toffee with a long creamy finish.\nCome explore Ferrari-Carano Whites and find your favorite bottle. Buy a bottle and your tasting is free.
LOCATION:85 Foothill Rd Ste 1 Reno\, NV 89511
SUMMARY:Ferrari-Carano Whites Tasting
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR